                                                                                                          Fee fee)

        Create asset create operation. For more options see class AssetCreateOperation constructor.

        Parameters:
        issuer - account id issuing the asset
        symbol - the string symbol, 3-16 uppercase chars
        precision - base unit precision, decimal places used in string representation
        description - optional description
        options - asset options
        monitoredOptions - options for monitored asset
        fee - class Fee fee for the operation, by default the fee will be computed in DCT asset. When set to other then DCT, the request might fail if the asset is not convertible to DCT or conversion pool is not large enough

        class AssetCreateOperation

      • update

        public io.reactivex.Single<ch.decent.sdk.model.TransactionConfirmation> update(Credentials credentials,
                                                                               java.lang.String assetIdOrSymbol,
                                                                               ExchangeRateValues exchangeRate,
                                                                               java.lang.String description,
                                                                               java.lang.Boolean exchangeable,
                                                                               java.lang.Long maxSupply,
                                                                               AccountObjectId newIssuer,
                                                                               Fee fee)

        Update asset.

        Parameters:
        credentials - account credentials issuing the asset
        assetIdOrSymbol - asset to update
        exchangeRate - new exchange rate, DCT base amount to UIA quote amount pair
        description - new description
        exchangeable - enable converting the asset to DCT, so it can be used to pay for fees
        maxSupply - new max supply
        newIssuer - a new issuer account id
        fee - class Fee fee for the operation, by default the fee will be computed in DCT asset. When set to other then DCT, the request might fail if the asset is not convertible to DCT or conversion pool is not large enough
